   - Changed postulate type from ∥ Σ[ B ∈ Booleω ] ⟨ fst B ⟩ ≡ BoolAlgOfCHaus X ∥₁
     to ∥ has-Boole-ω' (2^ (fst X)) ∥₁
     This preserves the Boolean ring structure (pointwise ops on X → Bool),
