2. Part11: ConnectedComponentModule
   - Replaced postulate ConnectedComponentClosedInCompactHausdorff with full proof.
   - Proof strategy (using equalityFromEqualityOnGenerators from freeBATerms):
     (a) From has-Boole-ω'(2^X), get surjective BoolHom Φ : freeBA ℕ → 2^(fst X)
         via BooleanEquivToHomInv ∘cr quotientImageHom
     (b) Generators: g_n = fst Φ (generator n) : fst X → Bool
     (c) D_n(y) = bool-eq(g_n(x), g_n(y)), where D_n(y) = true iff g_n(x) = g_n(y)
     (d) Forward (Q_x(y) → ∀n.D_n(y)=true): D_n(x)=true always (bool-eq-refl),
         then Q_x(y) applied to D_n
     (e) Backward (∀n.D_n(y)=true → Q_x(y)):
         - bool-eq-eq gives g_n(x) = g_n(y) for all n
         - ev_z(h) = h(z) is a BoolHom from 2^X to BoolBR (all pres fields = refl)
         - equalityFromEqualityOnGenerators: ev_x ∘cr Φ ≡ ev_y ∘cr Φ
         - For any E : X→Bool, surjectivity of Φ gives t with Φ(t) = E
         - Then E(y) = Φ(t)(y) = Φ(t)(x) = E(x) = true
   - Helper functions: bool-eq, bool-eq-refl, bool-eq-eq, ev (evaluation BoolHom)
   - New imports: Axioms.StoneDuality (2^), PresentedBoole (has-Boole-ω', BooleanEquivToHomInv),
     FreeBool (freeBA, generator), freeBATerms (equalityFromEqualityOnGenerators),
     QuotientBool (quotientImageHom, quotientImageHomSurjective, _/Im_),
     Cubical.Algebra.CommRing (_∘cr_, IsCommRingHom),
     Cubical.Algebra.BooleanRing (BoolHom), BoolBR,
     Cubical.Functions.Surjection, hPropExt, equivFun/invEq/retEq

